728650f-a.title: Richmond: Castleton Avenue - Caroline Street
728650f-a.text:
1110-1112 Castleton Ave., at the S.W. corner of Caroline
Street. Half the building (No. 1112) is occupied by one of the
James Butler Stores.
About 1927.
